defaultWhat should the BBC be for and what should be the purpose of public service broadcasting?
defaultFor
default nearly one hundred years, the terms of reference for the BBC have been tenable and broad enough to allow for the Corporation to develop and meet with success the challenges of new technologies and changes in culture and society.
defaultThere is and was no substantial reason for amending these 
