defaultThere should be, as indicated above, increased investment in BBC Alba, perhaps by doubling its budget.defaultWhat balance should be struck in what the BBC produces in-house, commissions externally and leaves entirely to others to create?
defaultThe introduction of the WOCC: the window of creative competition has led to a range of problems, not least the Brand/Ross affair where the form of outsourcing etc could have been said to be at least a contributory factor albeit small in the extent to which the programming was in tune with BBC values and standards
